'From Squeak3.3alpha of 11 January 2002 [latest update: #4734] on 1 February 2002 at 1:07:13 pm'!"Change Set:		prefDirRefix-mirDate:			1 February 2002Author:			Michael RuegerChange set 4668ServerCode-fixes-hg reinstalled an old version which forced the creation of a prefs folder on startup. This reverts to the correct version again."!!ExternalSettings class methodsFor: '-- all --' stamp: 'mir 11/16/2001 13:34'!preferenceDirectory	| prefDirName |	prefDirName _ self preferenceDirectoryName.	^(FileDirectory default directoryExists: prefDirName)		ifTrue: [FileDirectory default directoryNamed: prefDirName]		ifFalse: [			((FileDirectory on: Smalltalk vmPath) directoryExists: prefDirName)				ifTrue: [(FileDirectory on: Smalltalk vmPath) directoryNamed: prefDirName]				ifFalse: [nil]]! !